    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "everything is gone. the company, the funding, the house... it's all gone. i've spent ten years building this and now i'm just sitting here in an empty office watching the numbers hit zero. i don't even know how to go home. i can't face my family like this. i'm just a complete failure.",
